%BB%8Dc-th%C3%ADch-H%E1%BB%93ng-C%C3%A1t-ch%C3%A2u/poem-HrYvDephDpfYnIZl-V2i2g">Tống Cố bát phân văn học thích Hồng Cát châu - 送顧八分文學適洪吉州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Vi-Ph%C3%BAng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-L%C3%A3ng-Ch%C3%A2u-l%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BB%B1-tham-qu%C3%A2n/poem-OWVAemeEA6UazTOSnqx8sg">Tống Vi Phúng thướng Lãng Châu lục sự tham quân - 送韋諷上閬州錄事參軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/Tr%E1%BA%A3m-x%C3%A0-ki%E1%BA%BFm-ph%C3%BA/poem-4mnvnyA6k6RfA2JMT5OVyQ">Trảm xà kiếm phú - 斬蛇劍賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BB%AD-Hy-Nhan/author-_3sTvaRn7XDoRGq_884L9Q">Sử Hy Nhan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/V%C4%83n-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%E1%BA%A5n-V%C5%A9-chi-ng%E1%BB%A5c/poem-gpJ0z9eelL0PEF4D4-ViEg">Văn Trương Chấn Vũ chi ngục - 聞張振武之獄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/author-8k5-bGU03Z_txBNZHdLGbQ">Liên Hoành</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
